translate portuguese u20o_aa12b851:

    # "For now, I should go see Jez."
    "Por agora, tenho de ir ver a Jez."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:7
translate portuguese u20o_729f55a4:

    # "I drive to Jez's apartment and knock on the door."
    "Conduzo até ao apartamento da Jez e bato à porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:8
translate portuguese u20o_9f680c5a:

    # "It's late. I know Javi will already be in bed... but I have to see her."
    "É tarde. Sei que a Jez já deve estar na cama... mas tenho de a ver."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20o_80d9af52:

    # "After a few moments, Jez opens the door."
    "Passados alguns instantes, a Jez abre a porta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20o_ae0bc7cc:

    # det "Oh my God, [pcname]! You're back!"
    det "Meu Deus, [pcname]! Estás de volta!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:16
translate portuguese u20o_0eff94d3:

    # "I wrap my arms around Jez, holding her tight."
    "Envolvo os braços à volta da Jez, abraçando-a com força."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20o_6f4bce31:

    # det "I was so fucking worried about you."
    det "Estava tão preocupada contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20o_ff2a0b59:

    # det "I can't believe I let you go through with that."
    det "Não acredito que te deixei passar por aquilo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:19
translate portuguese u20o_02175897:

    # det "I wrote up a report for everything, but I didn't submit it yet."
    det "Escrevi um relatório sobre tudo, mas ainda não o entreguei."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:20
translate portuguese u20o_086ffc63:

    # det "I was afraid the whole department would think I'm crazy."
    det "Tinha medo que todo o departamento pensasse que sou louca."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:23
translate portuguese u20o_bc5af70c:

    # det "So what happened? Did you really go to another universe?"
    det "Então, o que aconteceu? Foste mesmo para outro universo?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:24
translate portuguese u20o_4859fa2f:

    # pc "Yeah, I did. I saw my dad."
    pc "Sim, fui. Vi o meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:25
translate portuguese u20o_856e8d4c:

    # det "Are you okay?"
    det "Estás bem?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:26
translate portuguese u20o_3c3fa8e3:

    # pc "Yeah, I'm great. I'll tell you everything tomorrow, I promise."
    pc "Sim, estou ótima. Conto-te tudo amanhã, prometo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:29
translate portuguese u20o_2ac0d825:

    # det "I'm just glad you're back."
    det "Só estou feliz por estares de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20o_61933f33:

    # pc "Me too. I'm sorry it took me so long."
    pc "Eu também. Desculpa ter demorado tanto."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:33
translate portuguese u20o_b55a59c5:

    # "She leans in and kisses me softly."
    "Ela inclina-se e beija-me suavemente."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:34
translate portuguese u20o_075b3c7e:

    # det "You have to cut that hair though, it looks awful."
    det "Mas tens de cortar esse cabelo, está horrível."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20o.rpy:35
translate portuguese u20o_bbdd1f3e:

    # det "Come on, let's get in the shower. You smell like a wet dog."
    det "Vá lá, vamos tomar banho. Cheiras a cão molhado."

